            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-6">About Us</h1>
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-700 space-y-6">
                <p>
                    GreenSource Garden Finder is dedicated to enriching communities through the power of gardening. Our platform doesn't just help you find nearby gardens—it's a bridge to a sustainable future, rooted in the wisdom of indigenous agricultural practices and the transformative potential of community green spaces.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">Our Mission: Sustainability and Social Good</h2>
                <p>
                    At the heart of our mission is a commitment to social good, articulated through our support for sustainable gardening that respects and revitalizes local ecosystems while providing food security. We champion the integration of indigenous knowledge into contemporary gardening practices, promoting ecological balance and biodiversity.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">Preserving Traditional Wisdom</h2>
                <p>
                    Indigenous farming techniques, honed over thousands of years, offer invaluable insights into sustainable agriculture. These practices, including companion planting and natural pollination, enhance yield and food quality without compromising the health of our planet. By emphasizing the importance of seed saving, we advocate for biodiversity and food sovereignty, ensuring that local communities maintain control over their food sources and preserve their agricultural heritage.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">Advancing Permaculture and Community Empowerment</h2>
                <p>
                    Inspired by the principles of permaculture, we view our environment as an interconnected system. This philosophy fosters sustainable and mutually beneficial relationships between humans and the earth. Community gardens serve as crucial hubs where individuals from all backgrounds, especially those in marginalized urban areas, can learn about sustainable practices, reconnect with their cultural roots, and gain access to fresh, healthy food.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">Supporting Food Justice and Educational Outreach</h2>
                <p>
                    GreenSource Garden Finder actively supports food justice by empowering communities to create and sustain their own food systems through community gardens. These gardens do more than grow food—they are also vibrant centers for education and cultural preservation. We provide resources and knowledge, making traditional and sustainable gardening accessible to everyone, particularly underserved populations who are most affected by food deserts and industrial agriculture’s shortcomings.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">Join Us in Growing Change</h2>
                <p>
                    We invite you to join us at GreenSource Garden Finder in cultivating not just gardens, but stronger, healthier communities. Our platform is a space for learning, sharing, and growing together towards a more sustainable and equitable world. Explore how you can contribute to this positive change, whether through volunteering, educating, or simply enjoying the bounty of your local garden.
                </p>
